===Formula E===
Audi will provide factory support to a Formula E team in partnership with DTM team Abt Sportsline. This team will be called '''Audi Sport Abt Formula E Team''' in the inaugural 2014/15 Formula E season.<ref>http://uk.reuters.com/article/2013/11/15/uk-motor-racing-electric-idUKBRE9AE0QQ20131115</ref>

